rows.label: fev01_110_150_msg0001
rows.name:
Right, I've got the accessory I wanted
and I'm all sorted for food.

rows.label: fev01_110_150_msg0002
rows.name: I think that should just about do it.

rows.label: fev01_110_150_msg0003
rows.name:
There's still time left before I have to
leave, so maybe I'll rest up at the inn.

rows.label: fev01_110_150_msg0004
rows.name:
I could head back to Gramps to rest,
but he might try to give me another
lecture, so...yeah, the inn seems best.

rows.label: fev01_110_150_msg0005
rows.name:
I have plenty of cash left, and it
can't hurt to rest in a nice comfy
bed once in a while.

rows.label: fev01_110_150_msg0006
rows.name:
The inn should be just past Rumbletum
Canteen. Let's get moving!
